item.title: Biometric AI Solution
item.description: Learn about Suprema AI’s biometric AI solution. Q-Face Engine Q-Face Module QFace Engine QFace Engine is Suprema AI’s artificial intelligence face recognition algorithm solution. Advantages of QFace Engine AI algorithm based on deep learning Retains large-capacity face data in Korea and abroad (25 countries, 10,000 people, 50M Images) Accurate data labeling with its own superior cleansing technology Deep learning-based face recognition solution using collected data Fast and accurate recognition performance Excellent detection/matching performance

item.title: Vision AI Solution
item.description: Learn about Suprema AI’s vision AI solution. Q-Vision Engine QVision Engine is Suprema AI’s vision AI algorithm solution. Provides video analysis algorithms for intelligent CCTV.
